Add upcoming and past events to your site on multiple pages. 


== Description ==
Add upcoming and past events to your site on multiple pages. Set the date and time.  Supports both one day and multi-day events.
You can also add other fields like event description, price, location, and more, and order events several ways.


== Frequently Asked Questions ==
=Can you change the order in which the events are arranged?=
Yes.  In addition to the default order, at the time of this writing, the plugin supports ordering events by date, title, and price.

=Does the plugin offer different date formats=
Yes, the plugin supports several different date formats.


== Installation == 
1. Upload the 'simple-events' folder in '/wp-content/plugins' directory.
2. Activate the plugin in the Plugins menu in WordPress.


